# Cloudflare Pages Redirects
# Build output directory should be set to "frontend" in Cloudflare Pages settings
# This makes files available at root: /week1.html, /index.html, etc.

# Clean URLs - serve HTML without .html extension (200! = forced rewrite)
/week1          /week1.html         200!
/week2          /week2.html         200!
/week3          /week3.html         200!
/week4          /week4.html         200!
/week5          /week5.html         200!
